name: WATERPROOF SKI BIB
description:
Ski bib made of technical fabric with three layers and protective membrane. Water resistant fabric against penetration of ≥5K. Heat fixed seams to improve impermeability.

- Elasticated and adjustable suspenders.
- Heat-sealed zip patch pockets at chest.
- Upper portion adjustable via heat-sealed zipper and side tabs. 
- Waist adjusts in back with adhesive strap.
- Hip pockets with heat-sealed zip closure.
- Utility pockets on legs with pockets and inner straps with different functions.
- Vents at legs for ventilation with heat-sealed zipper closure. .
- Reinforced inner hem to protect the area.
- Adjustable inner gaiters.
- Heat-sealed zipper closures at sides.
- Printed logo detail.

Zara Athleticz.

name: WATERPROOF RECCO® SKI PANTS
description:
Pants made of technical fabric with three layers and protective membrane. Water resistant fabric against penetration of ≥5K. Heat fixed seams to improve impermeability. Warm comfort in cold environments between 39.2ºF and -16.6ºF (4ºC and -27ºC).

- Adjustable and removable elasticated suspenders.
- Elastic waistband that is adjustable at the sides with adhesive tabs.
- Thermal polar fleece lined interior.
- Front pockets with heat-sealed zip closure.
- Reinforced inner hem to protect the area.
- Adjustable inner gaiters.
- Advanced RECCO® rescue system.
- Front zip and safety button closure.
- Logo print at legs.

Zara Athleticz.
